items.title: A very good reel
items.text: Sat with this for quite some time and I think it'll intrest you. It might sound obvious but I think it makes sense that we are drawn to people who make us feel seen. Maybe it's by talking to someone and realising they liked the same movies or songs growing up. Maybe it's by having a conversation about beliefs. It might sound obvious but I think realising this helps understand how to make people feel better whilst also showing why we might respond well to others.
